


{"id":2143,"date":"2016-04-19T13:20:41","date_gmt":"2016-04-19T12:20:41","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/?page_id=2143"},"modified":"2025-05-01T23:35:34","modified_gmt":"2025-05-01T22:35:34","slug":"zabezpeceni-auta","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/zabezpeceni-auta\/","title":{"rendered":"Zabezpe\u010den\u00ed auta"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"row product-detail\"> <div class=\"span6 \"><h2>Autoalarm i mechanick\u00e9 zabezpe\u010den\u00ed pro v\u00e1\u0161 v\u016fz<\/h2>\n<p>Kr\u00e1de\u017ee aut jsou bohu\u017eel na denn\u00edm po\u0159\u00e1dku a s dopl\u0148kov\u00fdm zabezpe\u010den\u00edm budete sp\u00e1t klidn\u011bji. A nejen to. Pokud p\u0159id\u00e1te zlod\u011bj\u016fm p\u0159ek\u00e1\u017eku nav\u00edc, z\u00edsk\u00e1te u v\u011bt\u0161iny poji\u0161\u0165oven <strong>slevu z havarijn\u00edho poji\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h2>Nab\u00edzen\u00e9 typy zabezpe\u010den\u00ed vozidla<\/h2>\n<p>Chcete sv\u016fj v\u016fz chr\u00e1nit proti kr\u00e1de\u017ei? R\u00e1di v\u00e1m pom\u016f\u017eeme s volbou zabezpe\u010den\u00ed i s jeho mont\u00e1\u017e\u00ed.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"article_header\">Defend Lock<\/h3>\n<p>Vybav\u00edme v\u00e1\u0161 automobil mechanick\u00fdm z\u00e1mkem \u0159azen\u00ed od \u010desk\u00e9ho v\u00fdrobce - Defend Lock. Lze ho instalovat do voz\u016f s manu\u00e1ln\u00ed i automatickou p\u0159evodovkou a je k n\u011bmu k dispozici 24hodinov\u00e1 asisten\u010dn\u00ed slu\u017eba po cel\u00e9 Evrop\u011b.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"article_header\">Autoalarm<\/h3>\n<p>Provedeme mont\u00e1\u017e elektronick\u00e9ho autoalarmu, kter\u00fd v\u010das upozorn\u00ed na neopr\u00e1vn\u011bnou manipulaci s va\u0161\u00edm vozem. Levn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed modely k tomu vyu\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed zvukov\u00e9ho sign\u00e1lu, alarmy vy\u0161\u0161\u00edch kategori\u00ed pak dok\u00e1\u017e\u00ed nap\u0159\u00edklad odeslat SMS, p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b obsahuj\u00ed tak\u00e9 imobiliz\u00e9r nebo GPS modul pro sledov\u00e1n\u00ed polohy automobilu.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"article_header\">Polepen\u00ed skel bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed f\u00f3li\u00ed<\/h3>\n<p>Provedeme polepen\u00ed skel bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed f\u00f3lii proti rozbit\u00ed oken. F\u00f3lie pat\u0159\u00ed k nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm zp\u016fsob\u016fm zabezpe\u010den\u00ed a p\u0159itom je to pr\u00e1v\u011b ona, kter\u00e1 zlod\u011bje odrad\u00ed hned v prvn\u00edm okam\u017eiku.<\/p><\/div>\n<div class=\"span6 \"><div class=\"motopress-image-obj motopress-text-align-left\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/zabezpeceni-auta.jpg\" title=\"zabezpeceni-auta\" alt=\"zabezpeceni-auta\" class=\"motopress-image-obj-basic mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right mpce-dsbl-margin-top mpce-dsbl-margin-bottom\" \/><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><!-- .row (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"content_box call-to-action-row \"> <div class=\"row \"> <div class=\"span12 \"><p>Pro konzultaci a mont\u00e1\u017e zabezpe\u010den\u00ed automobilu v <strong>Praze a okol\u00ed<\/strong> volejte <a href=\"tel:+420 608 313 437\">+420 608 313 437<\/a> (Po-P\u00e1 od 9 do 18 hod.)<\/p><\/div> <\/div><!-- .row (end) --> <div class=\"clear\"><\/div><\/div><!-- .content_box (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-fullwidth.php","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v17.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>